options(repr.plot.width=5, repr.plot.height=12)
sample_size1 <- dat %>% filter(variable_fac=='Singletons') %>% group_by(Color) %>% tally()
n_fun <- function(x){
  return(data.frame(y = -100,
                    label = length(x)))}
bipart_plot <- ggplot(dat,aes(EpiVal,value))+
                geom_violin(trim = FALSE,aes(group=EpiVal),alpha=0.8)+
                geom_boxplot(width=.1,outlier.color=NA,fill='white')+
                facet_grid(vars(variable_fac),vars(EpiState),scales='free',switch='y')+
                a+ylab('')+ xlab('')+
                stat_compare_means(aes(group=EpiVal,label = paste0("p = ", ..p.format..)),
                       label.x.npc=0.2, label.y.npc=1,size=3.5,family="Times New Roman")+
                theme_bw(base_size=20)+
                theme(legend.position='none',legend.title=element_blank(),
                      legend.text=element_text(margin = margin(r = 5, unit = "pt"),size=12),
                      panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
                      text=element_text( family="Times New Roman"))+
                aes(fill = Color)+
                stat_summary(fun.data = n_fun, geom = "text", aes(group=EpiVal),family="Times New Roman",
                    hjust = -1, position = position_dodge(0.6),size=3)
